    "We leave such topics as future work.",
    "Benchmarking models on device.",
    "In terms of on-device DNN benchmarking, there has been a rich set of literature in the past for edge and mobile deployment.",
    "Indicatively, Ignatov et al. [45] had been one of the first in-the-wild benchmark suites for on-device benchmarking and device ranking across a multitude of downstream tasks and modalities.Embench [5] quantified the different dynamics of model execution across various mobile, edge and desktop devices."
